-- Russia search of BP linked to Rosneft deal: lawyer
-- 
-- Wed Aug 31, 2011 5:28am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/31/us-bp-russia-raid-minorities-idUSTRE77U1FP20110831

 

 MOSCOW  (Reuters) - Russia's search of BP's Moscow office is linked to a lawsuit brought by minority shareholders in its TNK-BP Russian joint venture over BP's failed bid to team up with Rosneft, a lawyer for the minority shareholders told Reuters on Wednesday. 

 (Reporting By Vladimir Soldatkin; editing by  Guy Faulconbridge )